description.p:
In accordance with a particular embodiment of the present invention, the method of preparation of the track and electrical connector assembly comprises:
a) die cut at least one conductive support base;
b) fix the at least one conductive support base to a fabric support with a textile adhesive, preferably a holt melt adhesive applying pressure and heating from 80 to 185 Celsius degree, preferably 110-165 Celsius degree, for 5-30 seconds, preferably 10-20 seconds;
c) screen-printing a conductive silicone rubber on the textile fabric substrate while partially is treading in the at least one round shaped end of the conductive support base, applying a pressure comprised of from 0.2 to 0.8 Kg/m2.
